{"tid":2405312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪一定俾利是啲看更？佢哋憑咩逗我哋封利是？","createTime":"2021-02-12T09:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:18:02.000Z","uid":171902,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6bac747610d5d1abe089ae257a0a073a0fa1cc19","tid":2405312,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"屋企大廈有兩個入口，一個地下一個平台，平台個入口有個看更亭，但平時360日都係冇人喺個到，但每逄新年個星期就唔知點解會有看更駐守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似想捕住兩個出入口咁。班木咀平時見住我出入勁多野拎，開門制又唔識撳，夜晚返嚟成日見到佢哋條條死老野都喺到釣魚，一新年就勁精神又獻殷勤，幫手推埋門又講晒早晨。究竟佢哋憑咩逗咁多利是？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔應該養懶人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾啦孤寒鬼"},{"pid":"cc02baad020b4b67a956d473609cb1aee2e03b0f","tid":2405312,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"根本初一初二初三<br />\n班狗看更直頭同個鐵閘合咗體<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b3a2ec5e3cf64eebe1aa70f57ccf1188d6aefe","tid":2405312,"uid":54484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"算啦樓豬，你鍾意比咪比，佢哋都係打份工，大把人返工老闆唔係到咪又係諗盡辦法蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比果小小管理費唔好以為自己高高在上先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj